		<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><a href="http://www.loper-os.org/?p=988&amp;cpage=1#comment-3625">October 12, 2012 at 5:11 am</a></div>

		<p>I think that should be left up to the feedback of the individual broker sites?</p>
<p>If not, why only do shitcoins? You might as well have shitcoins for negative &#8220;dirty&#8221; bitcoins and rosecoins for &#8220;good clean&#8221; ones</p>

		<div class="reply">
		<a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='/?p=988&#038;replytocom=3625#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("div-comment-3625", "3625", "respond", "988")'>Reply</a>		</div>
