		<p>That might be interesting if you have the ability or requirement to &#8220;release&#8221; J within a pre-agreed time period, but it can be marked as &#8220;good result&#8221; or &#8220;bad result&#8221; when added to the network. If you get no answer at all when it expires, the bond gets marked as invalid.</p>

		<div class="reply">
		<a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='/?p=988&#038;replytocom=3641#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("div-comment-3641", "3641", "respond", "988")'>Reply</a>		</div>
